com.ciscowebex.androidsdk.phone

Class AdvancedSetting<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ciscowebex.androidsdk.phone.AdvancedSetting<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AdvancedSetting.ShareMaxCaptureFPS, AdvancedSetting.VideoEnableCamera2, AdvancedSetting.VideoEnableDecoderMosaic, AdvancedSetting.VideoMaxTxFPS

    public abstract class AdvancedSetting<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    A AdvancedSetting represents a setting item for a call. Each subclass is a setting item.

    These settings are for special use cases and usually do not need to be set.

    Since:
    2.6.0
    See Also:
    Phone.setAdvancedSetting(AdvancedSetting)
